Project no: 6

Project description:
A complete playable game with following features:
	- A player class that can move left and right, jump and shoot
	- Enemy sprites that uses observer pattern to avoid contact with the player
	- Projectiles ( spears ) that are used to kill the enemy sprites.
	- Object Pooling for the projectiles
	- Parallax Scrolling and Painters algorithm to give an effect of depth 
	- Explosion and 
	- Sound

Where I got my sprites: 

The background was taken from:
https://craftpix.net/freebies/free-halloween-2d-game-backgrounds/

