What sprite did I create (not Sprite or MultiSprite):
Knight -> This is the player who can be controlled by a, d to move left and right respectively 
ghosts and Zombie -> these are smart sprites that has AI. 
Spear -> The projectile.
Witch -> Simple Two way sprite for Painters algorithm

The easiest part of this project:
Implementing the painters algorithm.

Problems that I had in completing this project:

The player looses life if the player comes in contact with the explosion. Couldn't figure out a solution for this. 

Adding sounds threw an error. So I have commented out the lines that relate to sound. Please uncomment/comment if errors pop up. 

The following lines corrospond to sound:
engine.h	-> line 54
engine.cpp	-> lines 75, 264, 275, 339. 


Game Instructions: 
The goal of the game is to defeat all enemies. The enemy count is on the bottom left of the screen. Player lives are on bottom right. Avoid contact with the enemy sprites and explosions. Contact with explosions causes instant death. 

Controls:
A and D -> Left and Right
Space 	-> Jump
LShift	-> Shoot
R 		-> Restart
G		-> GodMode
E		-> Self Explode

